  {panel}

Generalize the mail harvester mechanism and enable it to push content into all kinds of content types in Confluence. Comments probably wouldn't make great sense, but it would be useful for pages and news items to have the feature. 

Use case for mail harvested to news item:

A site announcements page for a non-profit... the page itself would contain a {blog-post:time=7d} macro to display the most recent items.  But the items could get there via normal Confluence "Add News", or, for curmudgeonly content contributors, they could send an email to "annoucements@nonprofit.org" and be assured that their content would be "announced".

