I would like to see a macro that would display archived mail inline on a page.  This could be achieved through a {mail} macro with capabilities similar to  {blog-posts}; i.e.,

{mail:5}
{mail:5|content=from}
{mail:5|content=subject}
{mail:time=7d}
{mail:15|time=14d|content=excerpts}

or it could be achieved through {search} with some wildcarding capability and type=mail constraints....

