Is there a way to control the 60 min refresh interval of rss feeds from jira into confluence?

i have some rss feeds that are based on some intense querying in jira... and there is no need for these feeds to be updated every 60 minutes... it would be best if i could configure the feed so that it refreshes like say at midnight everyday. can that be done?

